Ported Jackett Torznab caps test oracle
=======================================

harbrr's Torznab caps oracle is ported from the Jackett project's test material,
used here as the offline parity oracle for the capabilities document (t=caps):

  - The category-tree + custom-id expectations and the search-mode
    supportedParams expectations are ported from
    src/Jackett.Test/Common/Indexers/CardigannIndexerTests.cs
    (TestCardigannTorznabCategories), reproduced in ../../caps_test.go as the
    in-memory definitions jackettCategoriesDef / jackettModesDef and their
    asserted tree / supported-param values (the jackett-port goldens
    caps/jackett-categories.xml and caps/jackett-modes.xml).
  - The caps XML grammar (element/attribute names + order, the audio-search
    mirror of music-search, the AllowTVSearchIMDB imdbid gate, the
    GetTorznabCategoryTree sort) is reproduced from
    src/Jackett.Common/Models/TorznabCapabilities.cs and
    TorznabCapabilitiesCategories.cs.

